<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <p>Dear {{ user ? user.fullName : 'Customer' }},</p>

    <p>Thank you for submitting your inquiry #{{ inquiry.inquiryNumber }} with Deckard. We have received your request and it is now being processed. You can find the details of your order below:</p>

    <p>
        <strong>Inquiry ID:</strong> {{ inquiry.inquiryNumber }}<br>
        <strong>Order Date:</strong> {{ inquiry.createdAt|date('d M Y') }}
    </p>

    <p>You can view the full inquiry details and track its progress in your account here: <a href="{{ viewUrl }}">View Inquiry</a></p>

    <p>We will keep you updated on the status of your inquiry. If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at [Support Email Address] or [Support Phone Number].</p>

    <p>
        Thank you for choosing Deckard.<br>
        Sincerely, The Deckard Team
    </p>
</body>
</html>
